<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="nord">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Unprocessable Entity - FlukeBase</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
</head>

<body class="bg-base-200">
  <div class="hero min-h-screen">
    <div class="hero-content text-center">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <div class="text-9xl font-bold text-warning mb-8">422</div>

        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Unprocessable Entity</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 mb-8">
          The request was well-formed but we couldn't process it. This usually happens when the data you submitted didn't meet our validation requirements.
        </p>

        <div class="alert alert-warning shadow-lg mb-8">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-current shrink-0 h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
          </svg>
          <div class="text-left">
            <h3 class="font-bold">What you can do:</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm list-disc list-inside mt-2">
              <li>Check that all required fields are filled out</li>
              <li>Verify that your data meets the required format</li>
              <li>Try submitting your request again</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
          <button onclick="window.history.back()" class="btn btn-primary min-h-[44px] sm:min-h-[48px]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
            </svg>
            Go Back & Fix
          </button>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline min-h-[44px] sm:min-h-[48px]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
            </svg>
            Start Over
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="divider my-8"></div>

        <div class="text-sm text-base-content/60">
          <p>If this problem persists, please contact our support team:</p>
          <a href="mailto:support@flukebase.com" class="link link-primary">support@flukebase.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
